<div class="jumbotron">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h1>Blocitoff <span style="color: #09f;" class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok" aria-hidden="true"></span></h1>
      <p>finish'em off, or ignore'em until they go away!</p>
      <% if !(user_signed_in?) %>
        <p><%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
        and get to-do'in, or Sign up!</p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <h2><%= link_to current_user.name, "/users/#{current_user.id}" %>:</h2>
        <% if current_user.items.count == 0 %>
          <p><em>fini</em>...super-dunzo <span style="color: #09f;" class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"></span></p>
        <% else %>
          <p><%=  pluralize current_user.items.count, "Things" %> To-Do</p>
        <% end %>
      <% else %>
        <%= render "signup" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Create <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil" aria-hidden="true"></span></h2>
    <p>Multiple to-do items inside mulitple to-do lists in
      multiple alternate universes!!  Okay, actually just
      the one... universe... for now.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Check <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-screenshot" aria-hidden="true"></span></h2>
    <p>Finished!  With extreme severity! Those tasks will think twice about
    not being done.  Pow! Right in the checkbox!!!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Burn tasks, burn <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-fire" aria-hidden="true"></span></h2>
    <p>Don't feel like putting certain fires out?  Eh, they'll go out on their own eventually.
    Give them a week they'll burn out. Meh.</p>
  </div>
</div>
